name: Ludwig van Beethoven
biography: Ludwig van Beethoven was a pivotal figure in the transition between the Classical and Romantic eras in classical music. He is regarded as one of the greatest composers of all time, and his works are celebrated for their intellectual depth, emotional expressiveness, and structural innovations.
